pudhu &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( english : new singer ) is a 1990 indian tamil drama film directed by s. thanu . the film features vijayakanth and amala in lead roles . the film , produced and had musical score by s. thanu , was released on 14 april 1990 . the film was initially titled theru &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , then changed due to some major reasons .